{"tid":1405144,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"因為之前有人反映前線後生問題 一股力量正在讓依場運動收皮","createTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T21:51:36.000Z","uid":57911,"like":40,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65819e9d4bf5bf1a4f1a4c955c28f52289dc5c3c","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:09.000Z","msg":"前線冇人想要贖罪卷！<br />\n邊個再捐贖罪卷大家見一個屌一個<br />\n前線要裝呀要人呀唔撚係要張卷呀<br />\n你派贖罪卷咪搞到走啲劉爵士咁嘅人出嚟佔便宜<br />\n大事大非我哋已經冇時間聲討依啲人<br />\n怕事嘅話最起碼嚟到你嗰區都企出嚟幫下口鬧<br />\n見到有危險咪立即返上樓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好擺底張卷當幫咗手<br />\n你張卷拖垮緊成個運動！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"134c586e6c9dc6befc2f03651c4454fc3e08186b","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9afe9b793f8c33b4dc22a5eb746f633884914e2c","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"c9805769a73b12bdae2ebbde55f5708a1aaa350c","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:46.000Z","msg":"推下熱門"},{"pid":"97290ce15122d450b7ecf028e52d393410efdf45","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:57:57.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"4bb334bafabf01a5c642b18c11d774e6daec920a","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:58:25.000Z","msg":"不要贖罪卷"},{"pid":"a5b3c7836427f4448f907dbab67ab90be6d74c77","tid":1405144,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"咪屌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有錢出錢 有力出力 <br />\n係咁多"},{"pid":"1f17027873fcf289d5392306096ab0dc6010d4c6","tid":1405144,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T07:58:37.000Z","msg":"不要劉爵士"},{"pid":"33934f49f8a1ff413696b84fa